Package: EliteProspectsR
Title: Package for scrapping data from eliteprospects.com
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matthew",
           family = "Palmeri",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "matthew.thomas.palmeri@gmail.com"
Description: Utility functions for scrapping various data from eliteprospects.com. This includes draft lists, player stats, player information, league information, and team information. Note that there is an IP-related rate limit, so will likely run into 403 errors when running lots of queries back-to-back. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
